  "answer": "AB : BD = 2 : 1",
  "explanation": "<img class=\\\"alignright\\\" src=\\\"http://www.gktoday.in/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/For-question-No.-5.gif\\\" width=\\\"159\\\" height=\\\"159\\\" />Let AB = 2x units\r\n=&gt; BD=DC = x units\r\n∴ AB : BD = 2 : 1\r\nHence option [A] is the right answer."
